Description: USB encryption enforcement daemon (bundled dependencies)
 A system daemon that enforces encryption requirements on USB storage devices.
 .
 This package includes bundled Python dependencies and does NOT require
 internet access during installation. Suitable for offline/airgapped
 environments.
 .
 Features:
  - Automatic detection of USB storage devices
  - Encryption requirement enforcement
  - User notifications via GUI
  - Integration with udev, systemd, and DBus
  - Configuration via TOML file
  - Bundled Python dependencies (pyudev, pydbus, typing-extensions)
